title: You HAVE To See What Priyanka Chopra Wore To The New York Fashion Week
text: While the seven day long New York Fashion Week is raging , Priyanka Chopra attended the Prabal Gurung show on Sunday . She sat in the front row wearing a high slit skirt and a black top, byPrabal himself. Keeping up with harsh New York weather, the actress chose to finish the outfit with some kickass suede boots and a fur jacket.
